VALUES
  ('medical-tech-moex-01227', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位70歲男性最近被診斷出多發性骨髓瘤IgG型，其檢驗報告如下，total protein 12 g/dL，albumin 3.3 g/dL， globulin 8.7 g/dL，IgG 7.42 g/dL，serum protein electrophoresis顯示46.2％的單一paraprotein波峰，請問其M- protein濃度為多少？', '["5.544 g/dL", "4.019 g/dL", "3.428 g/dL", "1.525 g/dL"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81f83a1fa077", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07950663439e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01228', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關單核球的特性，下列敘述何者正確？', '["是傳染性單核白血球增多症（ infectious mononucleosis）主要增加的血球", "離開周邊血液，移動至組織間，在數小時內很快即死亡", "CD14為其專一性表面標記", "在慢性白血球減少症（chronic leukopenia）的血中數量一定會減少"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81f83a1fa077", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07950663439e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 62, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01229', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關周邊血抹片觀察各種淋巴球 (lymphocyte) 形態的敘述，下列何者最正確？', '["小淋巴球 (small lymphocyte) 看不到細胞質者判定為B細胞", "大顆粒淋巴球 (large granular lymphocyte) 可以看到高爾基體 (Golgi body)", "非典型淋巴球 (atypical lymphocyte) 可以看到核仁", "漿細胞 (plasma cell) 可以看到奧爾氏桿 (Auer rod)"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81f83a1fa077", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07950663439e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 63, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01230', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關白血病最常見的年齡及實驗室數據的敘述，何者正確？', '["兒童：急性淋巴球性白血病（acute lymphoblastic leukemia），PAS(+)／MPO(-)", "老年人：急性前骨髓細胞性白血病（acute promyelocytic leukemia），染色體t(15;21)易位", "中年：多發性骨髓瘤（multiple myeloma），CD38(+)／CD138(+)／CD19(-)", "青春期：非霍金氏淋巴瘤（non-Hodgkin lymphoma），EBV(+)／Ebola(+)／HBV(+)"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81f83a1fa077", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07950663439e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 64, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01231', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關血液相關疾病、染色體與基因異常，下列組合何者正確？', '["Acute promyelocytic leukemia：t(15;17)／PML-RARα", "Chronic myeloid leukemia：t(9;22)／TEL-AML1", "Acute lymphoid leukemia：t(8;21)／BCR-ABL", "Acute myeloid leukemia：t(12;21)／CBFα-ETO"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81f83a1fa077", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07950663439e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 65, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01232', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-109-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關嗜中性白血球系列，在骨髓中儲存而形成"reserve pool"者，是指那時期的細胞？', '["Myelocyte", "Metamyelocyte", "Band and segmented form", "Hypersegmented neutrophil"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81f83a1fa077", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07950663439e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 66, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
